('notification-under-section-138-1-of-coss-2020','Authorisation of Compounding Officers under Section 138(1) of the Code on Social Security, 2020','labour_code','Central Government notification (S.O. 2362(E), dated 8 May 2026) issued under Section 138(1) of the Code on Social Security, 2020 read with Rule 54(1) of the Social Security (Central) Rules, 2026, authorising the ESIC Director General, Insurance Commissioners, Additional Commissioners and Regional Directors to exercise the powers of compounding officer for Chapter IV establishments.',null,'Ministry of Labour & Employment','2020','in_force',null,'https://www.dgms.gov.in/','Notification under Section 138(1) of CoSS, 2020.pdf',2,220,true,false),
